{"title":"阶乘求和","uid":"e0b859cd0bd48f530db5a5062dee6d93","slug":"阶乘求和","date":"2021-11-27T04:11:23.000Z","updated":"2021-11-27T05:39:08.160Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/阶乘求和.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h1 id=\"阶乘求和\"><a href=\"#阶乘求和\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"阶乘求和\"></a>阶乘求和</h1><p><strong>题目描述</strong></p>\n<p>求Sn=1!+2!+3!+4!+5!+…+n!之值，其中n是一个数字(n不超过20)。</p>\n<p><strong>输入</strong></p>\n<p>n</p>\n<p><strong>输出</strong></p>\n<p>Sn的值</p>\n<p><strong>样例输入复制</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><strong>样例输出复制</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">153</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><strong>思路分析：</strong></p>\n<p>题目要求需要求阶乘的和，我们的初步想法是定义一个<strong>求阶乘的递归函数</strong>，再定义一个<strong>主函数</strong>，通过<strong>遍历</strong>，1-n将数字传入fac中，之后 加到sum里。</p>\n<p><strong>注意事项：</strong></p>\n<p>1.采取自定函数求阶乘。用递归法。需注意递归法的尽头。（在本题中，fac函数的if语句作递归法的尽头，不可省略。）</p>\n<p>2.要注意最后结果的数值范围，避免溢出发生错误。</p>\n<p>阶乘很容出现<strong>数值溢出</strong>的问题，所以我们要<strong>扩大数值的存储范围</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">类型名称      字节数  取值范围</span><br><span class=\"line\">signed` `char`      `1    -128～+127</span><br><span class=\"line\">short` `int`       `2    -32768～+32767</span><br><span class=\"line\">int`          `4    -2147483648～+2147483647</span><br><span class=\"line\">long` `int`       `4    -2147483648～+2141483647</span><br><span class=\"line\">long` `long` `int`     `8    -9223372036854775808～+9223372036854775807</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">//long int   的简写是   long     占位符是：%ld   </span><br><span class=\"line\">//long long int的简写是   long long   占位符是：%lld</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"代码如下：\"><a href=\"#代码如下：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"代码如下：\"></a><strong>代码如下：</strong></h2><figure class=\"highlight c++\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"meta-keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"meta-string\">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">using</span> <span class=\"keyword\">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//设计的递归函数 返回阶乘值</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">long</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">fac</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> n)</span></span>&#123;        <span class=\"comment\">//long int 避免溢出</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(n==<span class=\"number\">0</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"comment\">//递归法到尽头 返回1</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">return</span>  (<span class=\"built_in\">fac</span>(n<span class=\"number\">-1</span>)*n);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//主函数</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">main</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"comment\">//思路:先设计一个函数求出每个阶乘</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> n;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">long</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> s=<span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tcin &gt;&gt; n;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i=<span class=\"number\">1</span>; i&lt;=n; i++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\ts += <span class=\"built_in\">fac</span>(i);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tcout &lt;&lt; s &lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 时间复杂度O(N)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//空间耗费多 能不用递归就不用递归</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>思路二（首选）：</strong></p>\n<p>我们看第第二次循环的时候也就是2!,此时等于前一个数的阶乘*当前数</p>\n<p> 第三次循环的时候，3!= 2! * 3</p>\n<p> 第四次循环，     4!=3! * 4</p>\n<p> 1*1</p>\n<p>1*2</p>\n<p>1  * 2 *  3</p>\n<p>我们可以退出 </p>\n<p>t *=i;</p>\n<p>s +=t</p>\n<h2 id=\"代码如下\"><a href=\"#代码如下\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"代码如下\"></a>代码如下</h2><figure class=\"highlight c++\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"meta-keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"meta-string\">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">main</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> n;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">long</span> <span class=\"keyword\">long</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> sum = <span class=\"number\">0</span>, t = <span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">scanf</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;%d&quot;</span>, &amp;n);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i = <span class=\"number\">1</span>; i &lt;= n; i++)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        t *= i;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        sum += t;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">printf</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;%lld&quot;</span>, sum);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>推荐这个算法，时间复杂度O(n)，但是空间占用小。</p>\n","text":"阶乘求和题目描述 求Sn=1!+2!+3!+4!+5!+…+n!之值，其中n是一个数字(n不超过20)。 输入 n 输出 Sn的值 样例输入复制 15 样例输出复制 1153 思路分析： 题目要求需要求阶乘的和，我们的初步想法是定义一个求阶乘的递归函数，再定义一个主函数，通过遍历...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.5k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"算法解题","slug":"算法解题","count":2,"path":"api/tags/算法解题.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%98%B6%E4%B9%98%E6%B1%82%E5%92%8C\"><span class=\"toc-text\">阶乘求和</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%A6%82%E4%B8%8B%EF%BC%9A\"><span class=\"toc-text\">代码如下：</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%A6%82%E4%B8%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">代码如下</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"一只菜狗","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"大概是还不够优秀，还不值得拥有。","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"socke编程","uid":"05485bbf2107f44cf3f643028e65f8ee","slug":"socke编程","date":"2021-12-10T02:52:11.000Z","updated":"2021-12-10T11:06:20.269Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/socke编程.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"text":"1 Socket编程 encode：编码 decode：解码 Python字节到字符串 (作为概念有必要理解)We can convert bytes to String using bytes class decode() instance method. 我们可以使用byte...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":983,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":